* {{rhymes|en|ɪvɪk}}

===Adjective===
{{en-adj}}

# Of, relating to, or belonging to a [[city]], a citizen, or citizenship; municipal or civil.
#: ''Thousands of people came to the '''Civic''' Center to show off their '''civic''' pride.''
